<plot>Set in Russia, in 1920, during the Russian Civil War. Andrei Shagan is a fisherman's son who is recruited by the White Russians to serve in the army of Baron Vrangel fighting against the communist Red Army. He saves the life of a Red Army officer Vlasov by hiding him in his father's house. The White Russians kill Andrei and arrest his father, but his family fights back with a suicide bombing.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?668220</url></doc>
